<h1 style="opacity: 1;">MEXICO</h1>
<h4 style="opacity: 1;">Real Mexico, none of that spring break Cancun bullshit. But actually, I'm kind of surprised that people in Mexico City don't know English well at all. Mexico is pretty weird... For one thing, they have a higher obesity rate than America (this is extremely apparent if you spend 10 minutes walking around Mexico City), and for another, everyone is extremely short. I mean even shorter than Asian people.</h4>
